OL,3,CMost neurodivergent homeowners find
OL,4,Chome-buying process 'too complex'
OL,6,FSeven in 10 (69%) neurodivergent
OL,7,Fhomeowners believe the home-buying
OL,8,Fprocess is harder for people in their
OL,9,Fsituation, a survey has found.
OL,11,FFeeling overwhelmed by too many
OL,12,Fchoices, arranging a mortgage, and
OL,13,Fneeding to have phone conversations
OL,14,Fwere among the key issues highlighted
OL,15,Fin a survey commissioned by property
OL,16,Fwebsite Zoopla.
