OL,3,CMost neurodivergent homeowners find
OL,4,Chome-buying process 'too complex'
OL,6,FNearly two-thirds (64%) of
OL,7,Fneurodivergent homeowners said they
OL,8,Fhad previously tried to buy a home but
OL,9,Fgiven up, with half (50%) finding the
OL,10,Fprocess too complex.
OL,12,FNeurodivergent people may have a range
OL,13,Fof conditions, including being
OL,14,Fautistic, having ADHD (attention
OL,15,Fdeficit hyperactivity disorder) and
OL,16,Fsensory processing issues.
