OL,3,CMost neurodivergent homeowners find
OL,4,Chome-buying process 'too complex'
OL,6,FProblems with the home-buying process
OL,7,Fthat people also reported in the
OL,8,Fsurvey included having to make big
OL,9,Fdecisions, sensory overload during
OL,10,Fproperty viewings and having to deal
OL,11,Fwith changing surroundings when moving.
OL,13,FSome 2-% found they needed someone
OL,14,Felse to complete the home-buying
OL,15,Fprocess on their behalf. Among those
OL,16,Fwho did it themselves, just over a
OL,17,Fthird (37%) completed everything
OL,18,Fwithout additional help.
