OL,3,CMost neurodivergent homeowners find
OL,4,Chome-buying process 'too complex'
OL,6,FZoopla and the Brain Charity have
OL,7,Fcreated a guide for estate agents, to
OL,8,Fhelp them understand the specific
OL,9,Fbarriers and additional needs
OL,10,Fneurodivergent buyers may have.
OL,12,FA guide for neurodivergent buyers has
OL,13,Falso been placed on Zoopla's website,
OL,14,Fwritten in partnership with the
OL,15,Fcharity.
OL,17,FDaniel Copley, a consumer expert at
OL,18,FZoopla, said: "The standout finding is
OL,19,Fthat most neurodivergent homeowners
OL,20,Fhave previously tried to buy a home
OL,21,Fand given up.
