OL,3,CMost neurodivergent homeowners find
OL,4,Chome-buying process 'too complex'
OL,6,F"With over half saying this is because
OL,7,Fthey found the process too complex, it
OL,8,Fshows there is a pressing need to
OL,9,Fadapt the guidance for neurodivergent
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FJayne Twiddle, an estate agent in York
OL,13,Fwho regularly works with neurodiverse
OL,14,Fclients, said: "Creating clear
OL,15,Fmaterials, not rushing viewings, and
OL,16,Fdoing what you say you are going to
OL,17,Fdo, when you say you are going to do
OL,18,Fit, are all critical."
